		<title>央行動態指引下，紐元兌美元匯率備受關注</title>
		<link>https://www.atfx.com/zh-hant/analysis/market-news/nzdusd-focus-central-banks</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[ATFX]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 23:23:37 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[市場新聞及觀點]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[NZDUSD]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[最近的新聞]]></category>
